OL,3,CFamily grieve sub-postmistress who
OL,4,Cdied in mental health spiral
OL,6,FFiona McGowan died aged 47 after being
OL,7,Fcharged with false accounting by the
OL,8,FPost Office, ITV News Correspondent
OL,9,FPeter Smith reports
OL,11,FOf the hundreds of cases we know of
OL,12,Fthose affected by the scandal, it's
OL,13,Fhard to imagine anyone suffered as
OL,14,Fmuch as Fiona McGowan and her family.
OL,16,FFiona actually had a proud track
OL,17,Frecord of running successful
OL,18,Fbusinesses in the Edinburgh community.
