OL,3,CFamily grieve sub-postmistress who
OL,4,Cdied in mental health spiral
OL,6,FDespite never having any problems in
OL,7,Fher previous businesses, she became
OL,8,Fone of the earliest victims of the
OL,9,FPost Office and computer system.
OL,11,FLike so many others, discrepancies
OL,12,Fstarted appearing in the balance sheet.
OL,14,F"Wednesday was the worst day of the
OL,15,Fweek - that was balance day," Gemma
OL,16,FMcGowan, her daughter tells me.
OL,18,F"It just kept mounting up and mounting
OL,19,Fup, until it got to #30,000."
