OL,4,Cdied in mental health spiral
OL,6,FFiona was charged with false
OL,7,Faccounting, and the Post Office
OL,8,Fdemanded she pay them the #30,000.
OL,10,FIn the community, her reputation was
OL,11,Falready ruined.
OL,13,FHer children remember they had to
OL,14,Fwitness their mum cleaning up the
OL,15,Fbroken glass of the smashed windows at
OL,16,Fthe post office.
OL,18,F"They would shout at mum, and called
OL,19,Fher a thief," says Gemma.
