OL,3,CFamily grieve sub-postmistress who
OL,4,Cdied in mental health spiral
OL,6,FThe stress of it all became too much,
OL,7,Fand Fiona's mental health
OL,8,Fdeteriorated. She was hospitalised,
OL,9,Fand put on medication.
OL,11,FUnwell, and fearing prison, Fiona also
OL,12,Fstarted turning to alcohol to cope.
OL,14,FAt this point, her two sons were
OL,15,Fremoved from her care.
OL,17,FGemma was over 16, though, so she was
OL,18,Fseparated from her younger brothers,
OL,19,Fand went into homeless accommodation.
