OL,3,CFamily grieve sub-postmistress who
OL,4,Cdied in mental health spiral
OL,6,FThey all saw their once happy lives,
OL,7,Fand their family, now ripped apart
OL,8,Fbefore their eyes.
OL,10,FThe cruel twist is that the criminal
OL,11,Fcharges against Fiona were ultimately
OL,12,Fdropped. Scotland's prosecution
OL,13,Fservice told ITV News, there was
OL,14,F"insufficient evidence" to proceed.
OL,16,FBut the Post Office still took the
OL,17,Fmoney from Fiona and the real damage
OL,18,Fhad already been done.
