OL,3,CFamily grieve sub-postmistress who
OL,4,Cdied in mental health spiral
OL,6,FHaving lost her livelihood, her home,
OL,7,Fher health, and her children taken
OL,8,Faway - Fiona finally lost her life.
OL,10,FShe went from running successful
OL,11,Fbusinesses to dying alone and
OL,12,Fpenniless in a homeless shelter. She
OL,13,Fwas just 47.
OL,15,FThe Post Office has told ITV News in a
OL,16,Fstatement, "We are deeply sorry for
OL,17,Fthe pain and suffering the events of
OL,18,Fthe Horizon IT scandal have brought so
OL,19,Fmany people and their families.
