OL,6,F"This can't just be whitewashed. There
OL,7,Fcan't just be apologies and CBEs
OL,8,Fhanded back. Somebody needs to be held
OL,9,Faccountable for this."
OL,11,FThe siblings have also been in touch
OL,12,Fwith Tommy Sheppard MP, who represents
OL,13,Fthe area where their mum's post office
OL,14,Fused to be.
OL,16,F"What happened in this case is beyond
OL,17,Ftragic and heartbreaking," he told me.
