OL,6,F"There is no doubt in my mind that
OL,7,FFiona's life fell apart and ultimately
OL,8,Fended because of the failures in the
OL,9,FHorizon system - she and her family
OL,10,Fare amongst the many victims of this
OL,11,Fscandal.
OL,13,F"I will now be doing whatever I can to
OL,14,Fget posthumous justice for Fiona,
OL,15,Frestoring her reputation and ensuring
OL,16,Fcompensation for her grieving
OL,17,Fchildren."
